{"tid":1276631,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[大整合] 和理非幫手的各種方法","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T15:24:57.000Z","uid":93753,"like":150,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4808088173b9ef9b99a4f5c32653595e611625","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:04:29.000Z","msg":"小妹睇左各類post , 加自己個人見解，整合左不同方法俾非勇士去幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勇士和理非，缺一不可！ 兄弟有新想法麻煩comment. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我分了三組:  A.課金. B.鍵盤戰士 C.身體力行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA.中產課金組<br />\n<br />\n1.課金立場新聞<br />\n 立場總編：捱得好辛苦，希望各位香港人可以盡量支持無金主的立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1274801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1274801</a><br />\n<br />\n立場新聞急需課金！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.課金港大民研 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21727/鍾庭耀-香港民研-特首民望-21730/鍾庭耀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F21727%2F%E9%8D%BE%E5%BA%AD%E8%80%80-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B-21730%2F%E9%8D%BE%E5%BA%AD%E8%80%80&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=87462757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21727/鍾庭耀-香港民研-特首民望-21730/鍾庭耀</a><br />\n<br />\n港大民研創辦人quit 左港大，依家獨立運作，急需大家課金！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.支持良心企業太古廣場    <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275701</a><br />\n<br />\n得閒去食下野，去great 買下野囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 課金各區本土民主組織<br />\n幫翻你地各區的本土民主組織啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兄弟麻煩留言補充<br />\n<br />\n5. 賄賂家中廢老，蛇齋餅粽政策<br />\n諗好左同家中親友講，區選投民主派就請佢地食餐勁既，唔洗同佢地爭辯，又唔洗晒口水，傷感情！ 一人攬一家老人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nB. 鍵戰組<br />\n<br />\n1. 思想工作做文宣，用理據文章支持勇士<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/64993?20190702&amp;fbclid=IwAR2_ZWGr6HA7Wxq8srUDp0V0vVzcYUfwkVKkwx4aqyL3yPgaWZrSuV4sXMs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F64993%3F20190702%26fbclid%3DIwAR2_ZWGr6HA7Wxq8srUDp0V0vVzcYUfwkVKkwx4aqyL3yPgaWZrSuV4sXMs&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=baab7d87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/64993?20190702&amp;fbclid=IwAR2_ZWGr6HA7Wxq8srUDp0V0vVzcYUfwkVKkwx4aqyL3yPgaWZrSuV4sXMs</a><br />\n<br />\n破壞法治的從來只有政府。<br />\n抗爭者破壞的極其量是法律，但爭取的是真正的法治<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 向身邊人宣傳好媒體，罷睇紅媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xtJHOsO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxtJHOsO.png&h=6ba5d3e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 做鍵盤戰士，打輿論戰<br />\n<br />\n#非常重要<br />\n#所有戰友準備聽日輿論戰<br />\n//明天輿論一定會大大力譴責示威者。請大家一定要幫手，盡力打入所有電台phone in節目，保住輿論//<br />\n<br />\n1⃣0800-1000 rthk1千禧年代📞1872311<br />\n2⃣0800 - 1000 商台881 在晴朗的一天出發<br />\n📞1872881<br />\n3⃣1700-1800 /1820-2000<br />\nrthk1自由風自由phone<br />\n📞1872311<br />\n4⃣NOW 事時全方位  星期一至五 上午9時30分<br />\n📞1833298<br />\n<br />\n可以簡短講：<br />\n-立場 eg支持示威者<br />\n-身分 eg父母/學生/示威者<br />\n-目擊/分享嘅事 eg你有遊行睇到啲咩，睇live睇到啲咩<br />\n-感受 eg傷心/難過/嬲/內疚<br />\n-*原因* eg因為愛香港/政府垃圾<br />\n<br />\nOptional:<br />\n-建議 eg問責下台/4大訴求/為示威者加油/普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nC.身體力行組<br />\n1.  反藍絲，譚詠麟。  <br />\n詳見下link<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1269387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1269387</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 關心自己的社區，可在自己社區 group 幫忙<br />\nFb group ,tg group 自行幫手吧。<br />\n兄弟幫手留言貼link plz <br />\n<br />\n3. 到建制派家附近遊玩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1272640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1272640</a><br />\n<br />\n唱下歌，播下歌，遊山玩水<br />\n<br />\n4. 老師作學校教育<br />\n做教育的巴絲，記住好好利用學校平台，係學校教學生明辨是非，保護自己<br />\n<br />\n麻煩請大家有橋繼續拋！係此貼留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力！我地不督灰不割蓆！雖然我地和理非有包袱未能一齊勇武，但我地都想係背後盡自己力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人加油，我真係好愛你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b743880bf666fbcf7fced6ef511ccdd7685b543","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"625ce842cd33c9f4fbc16762d83f796ef663ea94","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e632328c1cb0a95d8ca468e1202cc474d85d7cc","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"580e97285333b1f40a97d831d9e285a582def214","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04354939fcfd853fa43761798b05438a462ce5e8","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fd4762d8fee7c5fe86a7472f87aac68fe140afd","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82c88028b9c8895ebb9adda2c6edd73d1ef43d7b","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba97506a92524f28c7d7c4c7149169a11700e40e","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:06:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69217a0694fcb1b8ba45c2c4fa20ca49bf4dfcd6","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci