/eat2protecthk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Feat2protecthk%2F&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=2df7945b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/eat2protecthk/</a><br />\n<br />\n良心小店<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKShopvolution/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKShopvolution%2F&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=01cfee7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKShopvolution/</a>"},{"pid":"907682105b6c61b3f859f77b9d4442ddcf1aacc6","tid":1276631,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"仲有各大聯署投票之類!"},{"pid":"a3d61fe4c74dfc1225417cdbcdf986712d86c66e","tid":1276631,"uid":197636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:09:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"53621789673a9630e6caa40864865ffb4850c065","tid":1276631,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:09:41.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"940982aaab44483a27990afa0c0d7344a8785868","tid":1276631,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"推，但係我想知個港大民研會做啲乜？係咪又係話林鄭得三十幾分嗰啲？"},{"pid":"62da7d1060f7a7ccd10b03f606f20f204f39c134","tid":1276631,"uid":85980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1554e48f9664d1b8e3d0dc1f623f05613e5586d","tid":1276631,"uid":272458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:21:24.000Z","msg":"見無人推你<br />\n<br />\n打上電台仲可以儲定個list，之前fb已經有轉載過，類似係近年政府做過d pk野，鉛水，高鐵，沉降，沙中線鏍絲帽改標準。每一樣機制都「行之有效」，每一樣都無後果，引申到今日的局面，咁樣說服力會大d，也不會流於感情宣洩。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:13:34.000Z","msg":"＃轉載<br />\n<br />\n[轉載自新名校secrets] (有部份為後來補充的)<br />\n2003，被隱瞞的沙士。<br />\n2003，基本法二十三條。<br />\n2004，自由行<br />\n2005，領匯上市<br />\n2007，皇后碼頭事件。<br />\n2010，高鐵撥款，由669億超支至900億元<br />\n2012，國民洗腦科。<br />\n2013，香港電視攞唔到牌照。<br />\n2014，版權修訂條例草案（網絡廿三條）。<br />\n2014，「袋住先」篩選普選。<br />\n2014，新界東北撥款，暫時335億<br />\n2015，啟晴邨鉛水事件。<br />\n2015，銅鑼灣書局事件。<br />\n2015，三跑填海，由原本550億超支到預計1415億元，仍未完成<br />\n2016，DQ議員。<br />\n2016，港珠澳大橋撥款，由原本762億超支到1177億元<br />\n2017，國歌法<br />\n2018，割地兩檢。<br />\n2018，飛沙風中線。<br />\n2018，山竹「安全渡過」論。<br />\n2018，馬凱不獲簽證。<br />\n2018，被隱瞞非洲豬瘟疫情<br />\n2019，修訂逃犯條例 及 警察使用過度武力。<br />\n2019，中環海濱送中。<br />\n<br />\n睇清楚邊個先係真暴力。"},{"pid":"32d7bff91c3dee8aa16400ed8e0bcfc2ea3af1c1","tid":1276631,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"940982aaab44483a27990afa0c0d7344a8785868","tid":1276631,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"推，但係我想知個港大民研會做啲乜？係咪又係話林鄭得三十幾分嗰啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"佢係比較持平的民意調查"},{"pid":"1331c0669f38da6e2dedf8c50ea63579a4d879fd","tid":1276631,"uid":272500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:16:27.000Z","msg":"中產組仲有拋港元換美元現鈔"},{"pid":"572a3a7d9c6e23608fbb286321e37f6f5e23763b","tid":1276631,"uid":197636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:35:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"89361c666dcb9fe03a5d8791ff50ad3cddcb6ea1","tid":1276631,"uid":121985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:38:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b15c4d16c8f875bb105d28c8e08e160e3cf6e6a4","tid":1276631,"uid":216253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9a6e8297ea1e55a1847110bbffca03f0b7faa922","tid":1276631,"uid":28670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:41:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec64d42f9b77d65a2f720a81bf167b89bf1d89c3","tid":1276631,"uid":77030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6794d1ad0c262301c86a57eda66a6d12d70cc5b1","tid":1276631,"uid":77030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:48:11.000Z","msg":"推 冇發夢既請著黑